name: Travis Otto
description: I am an energetic, happy, active and sometimes “mysterious” man looking for a lady that is honest and caring. Life is too short to spend it alone…spending every day alone can be a real drag if you know what I mean. I do work a full time job but on my days off I would love to be spending time with someone who has some similar interests as I do. I am an animal lover, especially of dogs, but as long as it doesn’t have 8 legs and crawls (or of that general category) I’m pretty much cool with it
